(VERSION 1.2) (22/11-2009)

DE_Tudor_TWS, a map by The Wormhole Studios



A small village in the mountains is having a fruit festivale every year. But this year (2009) a group of terrorists have planned to bomb the village some days before the festivale. Their targets are the Tudor Square (B) or the village's communication central (A).

-------------------------------
INSTALL
-------------------------------

1. Put the files "DE_Tudor_TWS.bsp" & "DE_Tudor_TWS.nav" & "DE_Tudor_TWS.txt" here:
"C:\Programs\Steam\SteamApps\1245780\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps"

2. Start up Counter-Strike: Source and play DE_Tudor_TWS !
